description: Forecasters predict the storm will bring gusts of over 90mph (145km/h) in some areas.
title: Storm Ciara: High winds lead to disruption across Europe

maintext: Over in Denmark, a woman and a child had to be rescued from the North Sea after they were swept into the water while walking along a pier.
